00:16:04,821 --> 00:16:08,373
I-I don't know, for all
the, for all the time

353
00:16:08,375 --> 00:16:11,301
that you-you wasted on me.

354
00:16:11,303 --> 00:16:14,220
Come on, please. Here.

355
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:19,934
(DOOR OPENS, CLOSES)

